Section: misc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: "Dirk Thomas <dthomas@osrfoundation.org>"
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), ros-groovy-catkin
Homepage: http://www.ros.org/wiki/xdot
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: ros-groovy-xdot
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, graphviz, python-wxgtk2.8
Description: XDot, by Jose Fonseca, is an interactive viewer for graphs written in Graphviz's dot language. This package adds front-end capabilities to XDot including WX Widget support and a mechanism for receiving callbacks when nodes are clicked. This extension is provided as BSD.
